Handling Exceptions

    This example is a simple demonstration of how to handle exceptions
    under DOS/4G.  

    The example consists of the following files in the EXAMPLES\EXCEPT
    directory:

    EXCEPT.C    32-bit code source.
    
    MAKEFILE    Polymake-configured makefile for creating EXCEPT.EXE
                using Microsoft VC 4.x and/or Watcom.
